  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI have been monitoring geth with a simple shell script for a while.\r\nSometimes, \"pidof geth\" returns nothing when geth is up and running (PID did not change, nothing weird happens in geth logs or dmesg at same timestamp).\r\nI am wondering if this is expected or not and if there are some cases (not only for geth) of running process not reported by pidof.\r\n\r\nRegards,",
