    "body": "if the PID of geth doesn't change, then your problem is definitely with `pidof` or your Linux system. Geth doesn't have control over its pid.\r\n\r\nSorry we can't help you there. I advise that you check  the error code returned by `pidof` in your shell script, maybe something of significance will show up.",
